!   mqtthub.ecs

    script MQTTHub

    use mqtt

    dictionary Topics
    variable RequestTopic
    variable MessageTopic
    
    put `ectest/request` into RequestTopic
    put `ectest/message` into MessageTopic

    reset Topics
    set entry `request` of Topics to RequestTopic
    set entry `message` of Topics to MessageTopic

    mqtt hub
        client `EasyCoder-MQTT-Test`
        broker `test.mosquitto.org`
        port 1883
        topics Topics

    wait 10
    exit